Package: evaltools
Title: Tools for Creating LLM Evaluations with Tool-Based Tasks
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Sara", "Altman", , "sara@posit.co", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides abstractions for creating LLM evaluations that test
    language models' ability to use tools correctly. Includes factories for
    solvers, scorers, and dataset loaders that work with the vitals Task
    system. Supports tool name aliasing, YAML-based sample definitions,
    and LLM-as-judge scoring.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
